<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Giao Dịch Thành Công</title>
    
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Exo+2:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=Orbitron:wght@500;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">

    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #050505;
            --card-bg: #111111;
            --text-color: #a0a0a0;
            --neon-green: #39ff14;     /* Xanh lá Neon (Success) */
            --neon-blue: #00f0ff;      /* Xanh dương Neon */
            --white: #ffffff;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            /* Lưới nền Grid */
            background-image: 
                linear-gradient(rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 30px 30px;
            color: var(--text-color);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 50px 30px;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.1); /* Glow xanh lá nhẹ */
            position: relative;
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        /* Khung viền góc tech */
        .container::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0;
            width: 40px; height: 40px;
            border-top: 3px solid var(--neon-green);
            border-left: 3px solid var(--neon-green);
        }
        .container::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0; right: 0;
            width: 40px; height: 40px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--neon-green);
            border-right: 3px solid var(--neon-green);
        }

        /* Icon thành công */
        .success-icon {
            font-size: 5em;
            color: var(--neon-green);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--neon-green);
            animation: popIn 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            color: var(--white);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 1.8em;
        }

        .sub-title {
            color: var(--neon-green);
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #ccc;
        }

        .system-msg {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 2px solid var(--neon-blue);
            color: #888;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            margin: 30px 0;
            font-family: monospace;
        }

        /* Nút quay về */
        .btn-home {
            display: inline-block;
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--neon-blue);
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            border: 2px solid var(--neon-blue);
            transition: all 0.3s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .btn-home:hover {
            background: var(--neon-blue);
            color: #000;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--neon-blue);
        }

        /* Keyframes Animation */
        @keyframes popIn {
            0% { transform: scale(0); opacity: 0; }
            100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="success-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
        </div>
        
        <h1>Đặt hàng thành công!</h1>
        <div class="sub-title">// Nhiệm vụ hoàn thành</div>

        <p>Cảm ơn bạn đã tin tưởng SyberStore.</p>
        
        <div class="system-msg">
            > System: Đang xử lý đơn hàng...<br>
            > Status: Chúng tôi sẽ liên hệ sớm để giao account.
        </div>
        
        <a href="/" class="btn-home">
            <i class="fas fa-undo"></i> Mua thêm Nick khác
        </a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>